lass=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#控烟不是一个人的事#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hq8r90ilvtj20u019aq86.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OgPMC3YEM</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OgPMC3YEM</guid><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 08:00:41 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author><category>戒烟门诊治疗最快一个月戒烟</category><category>深圳控烟</category><category>控烟不是一个人的事</category></item></channel></rss>